title: Fonteez has launched!
content: Siro Enterprises is proud to announce the launch of our new clothing brand, Fonteez. Choose from five of the most popular typefaces from Bodoni to Helvetica in 3 unique styles and colors. For more information visit us at [http://fonteez.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018073905/http:/fonteez.com/ "http://fonteez.com") and answer the question…What's your type?
author: fonteez
